{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"網頁上的圖像","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/Guide/Graphics","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>現代網站或應用程式通常都配有圖像。我們可以很容易地使用<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>元素呈現靜態圖像 , 或藉由使用<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/background-image\"><code>background-image</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 設定 HTML 的背景元素性質。你常會想要建立動態圖像或在事後操縱圖像。這些文章將讓你知道如何達成這些效果。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"2d_圖像","title":"2D 圖像","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"canvas\"><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\">Canvas</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><em><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a> 元素提供</em> <em>APIs 讓開發者透過 Javascript 來繪製 2D 圖像.</em></p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"svg\"><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/SVG\">SVG</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><em>可縮放向量圖像(SVG) 讓你可以使用直線，曲線以及其他幾何圖形來編寫圖像。避免使用點陣圖像(bitmaps)，你可以創造出適合任何大小的圖像。</em></p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"3d_圖像","title":"3D 圖像","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"webgl\"><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/WebGL_API\">WebGL</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><em>一份 WebGL 初始指南，網頁用 3D 圖像 API。這項技術讓你在網頁內容使用 standard OpenGL ES。</em></p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"影片","title":"影片","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"使用_html5_影音\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/HTML/Multimedia_and_embedding/Video_and_audio_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">使用 HTML5 影音 (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><em>在 HTML 檔案嵌入影片及控制播放。</em></p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"webrtc\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebRTC_API\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">WebRTC (en-US)</a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><em>在 WebRTC 中 RTC 是 Real-Time Communications 的簡稱，讓瀏覽器客戶端之間(peers)串流影片/音效檔案與數據分享的技術。</em></p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"2D 圖像","id":"2d_圖像"},{"text":"3D 圖像","id":"3d_圖像"},{"text":"影片","id":"影片"}],"summary":"現代網站或應用程式通常都配有圖像。我們可以很容易地使用<img> (en-US)元素呈現靜態圖像 , 或藉由使用background-image (en-US) 設定 HTML 的背景元素性質。你常會想要建立動態圖像或在事後操縱圖像。這些文章將讓你知道如何達成這些效果。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Graphics on the Web","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Gráficas en la web","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Graphismes sur le Web","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"ウェブのグラフィック","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"웹 상 그래픽","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Gráficos na Web","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Графика для Web","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Web 图形开发","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/guide/graphics","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/web/guide/graphics/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web","title":"給開發者的網頁技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/Guide","title":"Web 開發者指引"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/Guide/Graphics","title":"網頁上的圖像"}],"pageTitle":"網頁上的圖像 - Web 開發者指引 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}